HEADWORD: Tartrelic
<hw>Tar*trel"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Tartar</er> the chemical compound.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or designating, an anhydride,
